{{version030}}
{{Flavour|Calls a surge of power from the earth, striking an enemy within the caster's sight. The spell cascades through nearby constructs, growing in strength with each one standing near the target.}}

'''Resonance Strike''' is a monster-only spell which strikes a target with [[smite-targeted]] accuracy. For every 2 [[nonliving]] creatures adjacent to the target, this spell gains +1 dice, doing from 3d(x) to 7d(x) damage. Examples of nonliving creatures include [[saltling]]s, [[peacekeeper]]s, and [[dancing weapon]]s.

{{monsters with spell}}

==History==
Resonance Strike was added in [[0.19]].

[[Category:Monster spells]]
